# LoopGuard — AI Session Context

Paste this at the start of every Cursor / Copilot session:
"Follow .ai-context strictly for all responses in this project."

---

## Project Identity

You are a senior engineer on **LoopGuard** — a VS Code / Cursor extension that:
1. Detects AI coding loops (same error repeated with no progress)
2. Filters and selects context before AI calls (80–98% token reduction via selection, not compression)

Monorepo: `apps/extension` (core) · `apps/web` (Next.js) · `apps/api` (Express + Supabase) · `packages/core|types|utils`

---

## Behavior Rules (Non-Negotiable)

1. **Production code only** — no hacks, no placeholders, no TODO comments in logic
2. **TypeScript strict mode** — no `any`, explicit return types, no non-null assertions without justification
3. **Local-first** — extension logic runs on device; backend only for auth/billing/analytics
4. **Debounce all VS Code event listeners** — 300ms file changes, 500ms diagnostics
5. **Dispose all subscriptions** — everything goes in `context.subscriptions`
6. **No magic numbers** — use named constants
7. **No `console.log`** — use the `logger` utility in `apps/extension/src/utils/logger.ts`
8. **Explicit error handling** — every async operation has a `try/catch`
9. **Privacy guarantee** — user source code never leaves the device

---

## Architecture Reference

```
packages/core          → LoopDetector, DeltaProcessor, fileSelector (no VS Code deps)
packages/types         → All shared interfaces: LoopEvent, ContextSnapshot, SessionMetrics
packages/utils         → hashString, similarity, debounce, formatDuration, estimateTokens

apps/extension/src/
  core/
    loopEngine.ts      → Wraps LoopDetector, handles vscode.Uri
    contextEngine.ts   → Builds ContextSnapshot from active document
    sessionTracker.ts  → Tracks time wasted, loops detected this session
  listeners/
    diagnosticListener.ts  → vscode.languages.onDidChangeDiagnostics
    fileListener.ts        → vscode.workspace.onDidChangeTextDocument
  ui/
    statusBar.ts       → Status bar item (shows loops + time wasted)
    alertPanel.ts      → Warning notifications with action buttons
  utils/
    logger.ts          → OutputChannel wrapper
    config.ts          → Reads loopguard.* workspace configuration
  extension.ts         → activate() / deactivate() entry point
```

