## Performance Budgets

| Operation | Budget |
|-----------|--------|
| Extension activation | < 500ms |
| Loop detection check | < 5ms |
| Context snapshot | < 50ms |
| Diagnostic debounce | 500ms |
| File change debounce | 300ms |

---

## Loop Detection Algorithm

```
Loop detected when:
  - Same error hash (uri + message + line) seen ≥ N times
  - All occurrences within the last T minutes
  - N = 2 (high) / 3 (medium) / 5 (low sensitivity)
  - T = 5 minutes (default)
```

---

## What We Don't Do (MVP Scope)

- No prompt history tracking
- No AI-powered suggestions (yet)
- No web dashboard (yet)
- No team features
- No backend calls for core detection
